                        "name": "Mangling Rend",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "A megaprimatus makes two fist Strikes against the same target. If both hit, the attack deals an additional 2d6 bludgeoning damage, the target is <a aonid=\"16\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">flat-footed</a>, and the target takes a \u201320-foot status penalty to all Speeds until the end of its next turn.",
